<span class="popup-jump-items">跳转到：<a class="popup-jump-bar" href="#Battery" id="cc1">控制器电池</a> | <a class="popup-jump-bar" href="#Other" id="A14">其他选项</a></span><div class="popup_jumpbar-line"> 
